State:
It is "Raw." We don't change anything, we don't fix typos, and we don't filter outliers.
Purpose: 
It serves as the "System of Record." If we ever mess up our logic later, we can always go back to Bronze and re-process everything because it's the 100% raw truth.
Analogy:
Bronze is the Unprocessed Ore fresh out of the mine.

